General.Name: Jayride Group Ltd
General.Description: Jayride Group Limited owns and operates airport transfers marketplace in Asia, the Americas, Europe, the Middle East, Africa, and the Pacific. It operates Jayride.com, an airport transfers marketplace that enables travelers to compare and book rides around the world through approximately 3,700 ride service companies and 1,600 airports in approximately 110 countries. The company was incorporated in 2012 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
